			<md-page>
				<md-paper class="el-paper" md-shadow="shadow-1" md-width="x12" md-position="center-x" md-padding>
					<span md-typo="display-1">1- Import materializer to your project</span><br>
					<span md-typo="header">Bower</span><br>
					<span md-typo="body-1">Minified (recommended)</span>
					<pre class="language-bash"><code>bower install materializer-min</code></pre>
					<span md-typo="body-1">Full size</span>
					<pre class="language-bash"><code>bower install materializer</code></pre>
					<span md-typo="header">Manual download - <a href="">Minified</a> (recommended) <a href="">Full size</a></span><br>
					<span md-typo="body-1">Note: extract on your project's folder</span>
				</md-paper>
				<md-paper class="el-paper" md-shadow="shadow-1" md-width="x12" md-position="center-x" md-padding>
					<span md-typo="display-1">2- Include the css and js files</span><br>
					<span md-typo="header">Important: include before every other css or js that overwrites Materializer styles and scripts</span><br>
					<pre class="language-markup"><code>&lt;head&gt;
    &lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="&lt;path&gt;/materializer/materializer.css"&gt;
    &lt;script src="&lt;path&gt;/materializer/materializer.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;</code></pre>
				</md-paper>
				<md-paper class="el-paper" md-shadow="shadow-1" md-width="x12" md-position="center-x" md-padding>
					<span md-typo="display-1">3- Load and initialize Materializer</span><br>
					<span md-typo="header">Note: you can choose a different variable name other than 'materializer'</span><br>
					<pre class="language-javascript"><code>var materializer = new Materializer(); // Instantiate Materializer on a variable of your choice
window.addEventListener('load', materializer.init); // Initialize Materializer on window load</code></pre>
					<span md-typo="header">Note: &lt;path&gt; is the folder containing the Materializer folder. If you installed it with bower, the path will be 'bower_components/'. Also, remember that the Materializer folder has '-min' at the end when it is the minified version.</span><br>
				</md-paper>
			</md-page>
